name: Baby Jey
description: '''Baby Jey''' is a Brooklyn-based indie rock band originally from [[Edmonton]], [[Alberta]], founded in 2015 by core members Jeremy Witten (guitar, keyboards, lead vocals), and Dean Kheroufi (bass, backing vocals). In 2017, Baby Jey started performing as a four-piece  band with the addition of Trevor McNeely (lap steel guitar) and Connor Ellinger (drums).
